'''天主教拉里奧哈教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Rioiensis}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de La Rioja}}）是[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教庫約的聖胡安總教區|庫約的聖胡安總教區]]。

教區於1934年4月20日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=II |year=1935 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=257-263 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-27-1935-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425134719/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-27-1935-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-25 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位於[[拉里奧哈省|拉里奧哈省]]，2004年時有265,350名教友（佔轄區總人口87.0%）、28個[[堂區|堂區]]和38名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-en|但丁·古斯塔沃·布拉伊達|Dante Gustavo Braida}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 13.12.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/13/181213d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716045238/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/13/181213d.html |archivedate=2019-07-16 |language=en |date=2018-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|羅勃·羅德里格斯 (主教)|Roberto Rodríguez (Bischof)|羅勃·羅德里格斯}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 09.07.2013 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/07/09/0459/01030.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716045632/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/07/09/0459/01030.html |archivedate=2019-07-16 |language=it |date=2013-07-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

